item.description: […] On the side, I’m aiming to be productive by collecting parts for future endeavors. I’ve been keen on Full Race’s FD manifold for a long time now. I do not reckon that it is the most widespread manifold in the RX-7 community, as most people opt for offerings from Rotary specific shops. Like me, initially, with my current A-Spec Short Manifold.
